sitemap-dupes

Build:
    go build

Run (one or more sitemap URLs):
    ./sitemap-dupes https://areena.yle.fi/sitemap.xml
    ./sitemap-dupes https://areena.yle.fi/sitemap.xml https://arenan.yle.fi/sitemap.xml

Output (stdout): one row per duplicate URL within a single sitemap file.
    <count>\t<url>\t<source-sitemap-url>
